// Quick overview:
//
// Pipes combine to form pipelines
// Pipelines and other atmospheric objects combine to form pipe_networks
//   Note: A single pipe_network represents a completely open space
//
// Pipes -> Pipelines
// Pipelines + Other Objects -> Pipe network

